languages.text: «Su culto de fanáticos de la sangre también existe únicamente por la tolerancia de{mf|l| la} Lord Capitán. ¿Qué tiene que decir a eso?».
languages.original_text: "Your cult of blood fanatics also only exists on the Lord Captain's sufferance. What do you have to say to that?"

languages.text: 「あんたの血の狂信者のカルトも、ロード・キャプテンの苦しみによってのみ存在するの。何か言いたいことはある？」
languages.original_text: "Your cult of blood fanatics also only exists on the Lord Captain's sufferance. What do you have to say to that?"

languages.text: “你们这些嗜血如命的狂热分子之所以还能活着，仅仅是由于舰长大人对你们的容忍。在这一点上，你有什么可反驳的吗？”
languages.original_text: "Your cult of blood fanatics also only exists on the Lord Captain's sufferance. What do you have to say to that?"

languages.text: "Euer Kult von Blutfanatikern existiert auch nur mit der Duldung des Lord Captains. Was sagt Ihr dazu?"
languages.original_text: "Your cult of blood fanatics also only exists on the Lord Captain's sufferance. What do you have to say to that?"

languages.text: « Votre secte de fanatiques sanguinaires n'existe que parce que {mf|le seigneur-capitaine|la seigneure-capitaine} la tolère. Qu'avez-vous à répondre à cela ? »
languages.original_text: "Your cult of blood fanatics also only exists on the Lord Captain's sufferance. What do you have to say to that?"
"Your cult of blood fanatics also only exists on the Lord Captain's sufferance. What do you have to say to that?"

languages.text: "Kan fanatikleriyle dolu tarikatın, yalnızca Lord Kaptan'ın müsamahasıyla varlığını sürdürüyor. Bu konuda diyecek bir şeyin var mı?"
